"Sets the permissions that are applied to files. The value is given in octal "
"and may have 3 or 4 digits. The SUID, SGID and sticky bit are not allowed. "
"To learn more about the file mode, you should read the <ulink url=\"man:/"
"mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> manual pages."
msgstr ""
"फ़ाइलों पर लागू की जाने वाली अनुमतियाँ सेट करता है। मान ऑक्टल में दिया जाता है और इसमें 4 "
"अंक होने चाहिए। फ़ाइल मोड के बारे में अधिक जानने के लिए, आपको <ulink url=\"man:/"
"mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> और <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> मैनुअल पेज पढ़ना "
"चाहिए।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2710 index.docbook:2720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: 0755"
msgstr "डिफ़ॉल्ट: 0755"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2718
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Option: <option>-F</option>"
msgid "Option: <option>-d MODE</option>"
msgstr "विकल्प:<option value=-F> -एफ</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2719
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Sets the permissions that are applied to directories. The value is given "
#| "in octal and has to have 4 digits. To learn more about the directory mode "
#| "(dir_mode), you should read the <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
#| "\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
#| "manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and <ulink url=\"man:/"
#| "umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
#| "refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> manual "
#| "pages."
msgid ""
"Sets the permissions that are applied to directories. The value is given in "
"octal and may have 3 or 4 digits. The SUID, SGID and sticky bit are not "
"allowed. To learn more about the directory mode, you should read the <ulink "
"url=\"man:/mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> manual pages."
msgstr ""
"निर्देशिकाओं पर लागू होने वाली अनुमतियाँ सेट करता है। मान ऑक्टल में दिया जाता है और इसमें 4 "
"अंक होने चाहिए। निर्देशिका मोड (dir_mode) के बारे में अधिक जानने के लिए, आपको <ulink "
"url=\"man:/mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> और <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> मैनुअल पेज पढ़ना "
"चाहिए।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Character Sets"
msgstr "वर्ण सेट"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use character sets"
msgstr "वर्ण सेट का उपयोग करें"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2735
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Option: <option>-F</option>"
msgid "Option: <option>-E cs1:cs2</option>"
msgstr "विकल्प:<option value=-F> -एफ</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2736
#, no-c-format
